snippet.title: NinjaFall reveal trailer.
snippet.description:
NinjaFall is coming soon to steam. Come take a first look at the arcade action inspired by the likes of TowerFall and your favourite shonen ninjas.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2169760/NinjaFall/
